            <h2>Who we serve</h2>
            <div class="row align">
              <div class="col brdr">
                <h3>Individuals</h3>
                <img src="public\assets\feature1.jpg" height="60%" width="70%" alt="">
                <p>
                  Fit N Sync provides preset workout templates for individuals confused about
                  different exercises along with video demonstration. Users can also
                  create their own templates and view a report after finishing
                  workouts and get recommendations on latest sets
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col brdr">
                <h3>Gyms</h3>
                <img src="public\assets\feature2.jpg" height="60%" width="70%"alt="">
