                  Fit N Sync has a feature where gyms can setup there own platforms and users
                  in that particular gym can join and share there progress. Coaches
                  can share the notices along with pushing a reminder regarding any
                  payments pending.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col brdr">
                <h3>Coaches</h3>
                <img src="public\assets\feature3.jpg" height="60%" width="70%" alt="">
                <p>
                  Fit N Sync also supports coach profile where users can register themselves
                  as coaches and post their achievements for the gym goers. user can
                  then pay the coaches for personal training where coaches can enjoy
                  all features of the app and provide users with custom templates.
                </p>
